commit 273caa260035c03d89ad63d72d8cd3d9e5c5e3f1 upstream.

If the device is of type VFL_TYPE_SUBDEV then vdev->ioctl_ops
is NULL so the 'if (!ops->vidioc_query_ext_ctrl)' check would crash.
